data.name: TEXT_AMPWIZARD_HELP_GENERAL_INFO
data.value:
A Decision is used to analyze usage records (rated billing records) and possibly modify charges on the basis of this analysis. Decisions are necessary when it is impossible to determine the amount by examining a single isolated record.
For example, you may want to give a special rate if the number of telephone minutes used during the month is > 1000. You can only determine the rate to use after adding up all the usage records. If the minutes are > 1000, then for each record the rate is changed and a new charge amount is calculated.(German)

data.name: TEXT_AMPWIZARD_HELP_ITEMS_TO_AGGREGATE
data.value: (GERMAN) For example, suppose the Decision Type is \"Use a special rate if the number of minutes of usage is over 500\". The settings might include \"500\" and the \"special rate\" to apply.

data.name: TEXT_AMPWIZARD_HELP_AGGREGATION_METHOD
data.value: (GERMAN) Decisions are used when a monetary charge amount cannot be calculated by looking at a single record. Instead, many usage records must be examined and a total must be the number of events, units of usage, or charge amounts. The total, or aggregate, is then used to help determine the charge amount.

data.name: TEXT_AMPWIZARD_HELP_AGGREGATION_METHOD_ADD_UP_MONETARY_CHARGE
data.value: (GERMAN) Example: \"Apply a discount if there's over $100 in charges.\"

data.name: TEXT_AMPWIZARD_HELP_AGGREGATION_METHOD_ADD_UP_UNIT_OF_USAGE
data.value: (GERMAN) Example: \"Use a special rate if over 1,000 minutes.\"

data.name: TEXT_AMPWIZARD_HELP_AGGREGATION_METHOD_COUNT_NUMBER_OF_EVENTS
data.value: (GERMAN) Example: \"Apply a discount if over 100 calls were made.\"

data.name: TEXT_AMPWIZARD_HELP_AGGREGATION_METHOD_FROM_PARAMETER_TABLE
data.value: (GERMAN) Usage is aggregated based on the value set in the parameter table.

data.name: TEXT_AMPWIZARD_HELP_MULTIBUCKET
data.value: (German)Act on each individual record. Usage may have different prices which are determined by the bucket into which they fall.

data.name: TEXT_AMPWIZARD_HELP_SINGLEBUCKET
data.value: (German)Act on all the records together. All usage has same price which is determined by total volume.

data.name: TEXT_AMPWIZARD_HELP_NO_CHARGE
data.value: (German) Do not generate a charge for this decision
